<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Dumbbell-Zottman-Preacher-Curl">Dumbbell Zottman Preacher Curl</h3>



<p>The <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/dumbbell-zottman-preacher-curl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">dumbbell Zottman preacher curl</a> is a preacher curl with a twist. The setup remains the same, as your triceps rest firmly on the pad. However, the use of dumbbells allows your wrists to rotate, targeting the forearms.</p>



<p>The primary movers are the biceps long heads and the biceps short heads. The secondary movers are the brachialis, brachioradialis, wrist flexors, and wrist extensors.</p>



<p>Performing the dumbbell Zottman is a time-efficient movement, allowing you to target the upper arms and forearms. Performing with enough resistance can overload the forearms throughout the full range of motion promoting muscle growth.&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio vimeo-custom"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
