<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Tips&nbsp;</h4>



<ul>
<li>Ensure your core is tensed and your feet are firmly placed on the ground. This will create a stable base and improve your lifting capacity.</li>



<li>Concentrate on tensing your biceps, and controlling the movement through the lifting and lower phases.</li>
</ul>



